videos.description: DeMar DeRozan knifes through the paint between Rockets defenders to draw the contact and sink the layup for a chance at a 3-point play.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (DeRozan slices through the paint for and-1 bucket) 2020/12/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: DeRozan slices through the paint for and-1 bucket

videos.description: James Harden throws a slick between the legs pass while on the run into the hands of Christian Wood for the finesse finish at the rim for the Rockets.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Harden goes between the legs to Wood for lay-in) 2020/12/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harden goes between the legs to Wood for lay-in

videos.description: The Rockets go on to defeat the Spurs 128-106 in their fourth preseason game behind the double-double effort of Christian Wood with 27 points and 10 rebounds.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (Christian Wood tallies 27-point double-double in preseason game vs. Spurs) 2020/12/17 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Christian Wood tallies 27-point double-double in preseason game vs. Spurs

videos.description: Christian Wood grabs a rebound and goes the other way to score on a nice finish, prompting Rockets announcer Bill Worrell to ask, "Who needs James Harden?"

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Rockets announcer says, 'Who needs James Harden?' after Christian Wood bucket) 2020/12/18 ESHEET
